{"type":"message","id":"15475f2b","parentId":"fc8ccfa2","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:19:29.320Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-04-01 13:19 GMT-3] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Research whether the current S1 scene_director contract/design is demanding too much precision from a semantic agent. Focus on practical patterns: agent decides scene grouping but deterministic code derives exact spans/text alignment afterward. Summarize whether this would be a better design than forcing the agent to emit exact start_word/end_word plus exact narration spans. Repo context: C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory."}],"timestamp":1775060369299}}
